  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK986">
<l>cālpiṟkuk kaṭṭaḷai yāteṉiṟ ṟōlvi</l>
<l>tulaiyallār kaṇṇuṅ koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The touch-stone of perfection is to receive a defeat even at the hands of one's inferiors.</l>
            </lg>
